text: Marta Majowska (17 July 1911 - 17 February 2001) was a Polish gymnast. She competed in the women's artistic team all-around event at the 1936 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1911 births Category:2001 deaths Category:Polish female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Poland Category:Gymnasts at the 1936 Summer Olympics Category:People from Chorzów
